## Description {#details}

Errors of this type should be returned if a module fails to include definitions that are claimed by the module&#39;s associated <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/orc/materializationresponsibility">MaterializationResponsibility</a>.

If this error is returned it is indicative of a broken transformation / compiler / object cache.
